013) to\ntime series based on a variant of Stein's method developed therein.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jun 2014 13:22:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Aug 2014 04:33:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-12"}
